content:
You are inspiring and kind and 💯legit! Proud to know you!  #Repost @loufemia (@get_repost)
・・・
Haha Blowing up the news. Thank you to my great friend and one of the best people I know, Amy Freeze for letting me tell my story. Anyone who knows me knows I have been to hell and back...and now I couldn't be happier with how great I'm doing, my progress, outlook and where I am at with this journey. I've gotten countless messages telling me how I've inspired them to not give up when it got hard for whatever disease or experience they r dealing with. If I can repost this and one person is helped because of my story then it's all worth it to me. Be your own SUPERHERO in life. Cure MS. Motivate, inspire and spread good vibes... Start by doing what's necessary, then do what's possible; and suddenly you are doing the impossible. Make a difference...pay it forward , inspire and motivate. Do something bigger than yourself. I went from not walking to this. This was for a great charity, cause and ms awareness 👍🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻
#Multiplesclerosis, or #MS, is a long-lasting disease that can affect your brain, spinal cord, and the optic nerves in your eyes. It can cause problems with vision, balance, muscle control, and other basic body functions. MS happens when your immune system attacks a fatty material called myelin, which wraps around your nerve fibers to protect them. Without this outer shell, your nerves become damaged. Scar tissue may form. 
Never give up, push yourself and never let anyone tell u that u can't do something, ever!! They tell u that just because they can't do it themselves. Be strong and always have hope. Keep #family close, be active have positive energy and be stress free !!! Don't let it stop you....🙌🏻👍🏻👊🏻#inspiration#life#love#disease#ms#multiplesclerosis#fuckms#abc7ny#fitness#fitfam#tattoo#tattoos#ink#inked#tatted#instafit#nyc#usa#fit#fitlife#fitness#latergram#motivation#trendywendy#blessed#godbless#bjj 🔥🔥🇺🇸 🇺🇸 💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻#repost @amyfreeze @wendyshow @theellenshow  @abc7ny
